sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant CarController
    participant JWTAuth as JWT Authenticator
    participant CarService
    participant CarRepository
    participant Database

    Client->>CarController: POST /cars (met JWT token)
    CarController->>JWTAuth: authenticate()

    alt Token geldig
        JWTAuth->>JWTAuth: Valideer JWT token
        JWTAuth->>CarController: JWTPrincipal
        CarController->>CarController: Haal ownerId uit JWT claims

        alt Request body valide
            CarController->>CarController: receive<CarCreateOrUpdateRequest>()
            CarController->>CarService: createCar(request, ownerId)
            CarService->>CarRepository: save(car)
            CarRepository->>Database: INSERT INTO cars
            Database-->>CarRepository: Success
            CarRepository-->>CarService: newCar
            CarService-->>CarController: newCar
            CarController-->>Client: 201 Created + newCar
        else Request body invalide
            CarController-->>Client: 400 Bad Request
        end

    else Token ongeldig
        JWTAuth-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    alt Database error
        CarRepository-->>CarService: null
        CarService-->>CarController: null
        CarController-->>Client: 500 Internal Server Error
    end